Detailed Description

cvmx_pcs::_mr::_control_reg

NOTE: Whenever AN_EN bit[12] is set, Auto negotiation is allowed to happen. The results of the auto negotiation process set the fields in the AN_RESULTS reg. When AN_EN is not set, AN_RESULTS reg is don't care. The effective SPD, DUP etc.. get their values from the pcs_mr_ctrl reg.
